22 SUMMARY
2233 This amendment removes the provision in the bill allowing the simultaneous use of
2244 manufacturing-related equipment, supplies and facilities for the manufacturing of cannabis
2255 products and hemp products. It also adds the use of cannabis concentrate in the creation of
2266 cannabis vape cartridges and the use of cannabis flower and cannabis trim in the creation
2277 of prerolled cannabis cigarettes to the activities that are not considered to be the type of
2288 further processing, manufacturing or alteration that requires additional testing of the
2299 cannabis or cannabis product. The amendment also adds an appropriations and allocations
3300 section.
